| History                 = The Dark Council is an alliance of different beings from the [[Ten Realms]] with the objective to spread conflict for their personal gain.

Their first act of war was the massacre of the [[Light Elves]] of [[Alfheim]], an event Malekith expected would surely bring the attention of [[Jane Foster (Earth-616)|Thor]]. Because of this, they tasked one person that was seeking admittance in the council, [[Loki Laufeyson (Ikol) (Earth-616)|Loki]], with carrying out the murder of the Goddess of Thunder.{{r|Mighty Thor Vol 3 1}}

